===[[Pokémon Trading Card Game Pocket]]===
{{main|Brock (Genetic Apex 224)}}
Brock makes an appearance as a {{TCG|Supporter}} card in [[Pokémon Trading Card Game Pocket]]'s first expansion, {{TCGP|Genetic Apex}}. When the player plays this card, they can take a {{TCG|Fighting}} {{TCG|Energy}} from their Energy Zone and attach it any card named {{TCGP|Golem}} or {{TCGP|Onix}}.

